body_html: @jeffheaton I'm having the same issue with DNNClassifier and SKCompat. It would help if the tf.contrib.learn Quickstart tutorial were updated to reflect the use of SKcompat rather than the deprecated version that it currently uses (see https://www.tensorflow.org/get_started/tflearn).
